author: grkvlt
msg: NO-JIRA: Update version and broker constants for tests
Setup more version constants in QpidBrokerTestCase and update test-profiles
to explicitly set versions. Creates 0-8 and 0-10 version profiles, and sets
the default protocol version to be 0-9-1 for the others. Protocol version
negotiation is accomplished under the Java profiles by disabling versions
on the ports the broker is listening on.
